mpls ip
no shutdown
int s1/2
ip address 10.98.200.10 255.255.255.254
description FR-W02 TO CH-W01
mpls ip
no shutdown

int g3/0
ip address 10.98.210.4 255.255.255.254
description FR-W02 TO FR-CE-01
no shutdown
int g4/0
ip address 10.98.210.6 255.255.255.254
